fj.test
Class Arbitrary<A>

java.lang.Object
  fj.test.Arbitrary<A>

public final class Arbitrary<A>
extends java.lang.Object

The type used to generate arbitrary values of the given type parameter (A). Common arbitrary implementations are provided.
